le summarizes the funded status of the postretirement plans, which corresponds to the amounts", "bbox": [104.2, 1075.4, 1148.6, 1098.7]}, {"text": "recognized in the balance sheets at December 31, 2018, and December 31, 2017.", "bbox": [104.2, 1100.4, 861.6, 1123.7]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [110.4, 1143.8, 205.3, 1160.1]}, {"text": "in millions", "bbox": [110.4, 1164.6, 174.4, 1180.9]}, {"text": "2018", "bbox": [904.6, 1164.6, 937.0, 1180.9]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [1071.3, 1164.6, 1103.7, 1180.9]}, {"text": "Funded status (a)", "bbox": [110.4, 1183.1, 218.5, 1201.7]}, {"text": "$", "bbox": [843.8, 1185.4, 851.9, 1201.7]}, {"text": "(17) $", "bbox": [978.1, 1185.4, 1018.5, 1201.7]}, {"text": "(16)", "bbox": [1144.8, 1185.4, 1170.8, 1201.7]}, {"text": "Accrued postretirement benefit cost recognized (b)", "bbox": [110.4, 1203.9, 430.8, 1222.6]}, {"text": "(17)", "bbox": [978.1, 1206.3, 1004.1, 1222.6]}, {"text": "(16)", "bbox": [1144.8, 1206.3, 1170.8, 1222.6]}, {"text": "(a)", "bbox": [104.2, 1227.1, 122.9, 1241.1]}, {"text": "The shortage of the FVA under the APBO.", "bbox": [141.7, 1227.1, 373.5, 1241.1]}, {"text": "(b)", "bbox": [104.2, 1242.1, 122.9, 1256.1]}, {"text": "Consists entirely of noncurrent liabilities.", "bbox": [141.7, 1242.1, 364.7, 1256.1]}, {"text": "There are no regulations that require contributions to the VEBA trust that funds our retiree healthcare plan, so there", "bbox": [104.2, 1284.6, 1169.6, 1307.9]}, {"text": "is no minimum funding requirement. We are permitted to make discretionary contributions to the VEBA trust, subject", "bbox": [104.2, 1309.6, 1176.0, 1332.9]}, {"text": "to certain IRS restrictions and limitations. We anticipate that our discretionary contributions in 2019, if any, will be", "bbox": [104.2, 1334.6, 1146.7, 1357.9]}, {"text": "minimal.", "bbox": [104.2, 1359.6, 181.7, 1382.9]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2018, we expect to pay the benefits from other postretirement plans as follows: 2019 — $5 million;", "bbox": [104.2, 1409.6, 1176.5, 1432.9]}, {"text": "2020 — $5 million; 2021 — $5 million; 2022 — $5 million; 2023 — $5 million; and $22 million in the aggregate from", "bbox": [104.2, 1434.6, 1167.3, 1457.9]}, {"text": "2024 through 2028.", "bbox": [104.2, 1459.6, 284.9, 1482.9]}, {"text": "To determine the APBO, we assumed discount rates of 4.00% at December 31, 2018, and 3.5% at December 31,", "bbox": [104.2, 1509.6, 1151.0, 1532.9]}, {"text": "2017.", "bbox": [104.2, 1534.6, 156.3, 1557.9]}]}